## Constraints

- Do NOT write any code. This is planning only.
- Every domain must have at least one identified consumer.
- Migration sequence must order by ascending risk.
- No domain should depend on an unmigrated domain in its position in the sequence.
- Prohibitions (Rank 1) CANNOT be violated during migration — flag any plan that would violate them.
- Do not execute arbitrary Python code in Jinja2 expressions (sandboxed execution).
- Handle missing variables gracefully (leave as-is or use default if specified).

